OL,3,CFresh bin strike as agency workers say
OL,4,Cthey're being bullied and threatened
OL,6,FAgency refuse workers in Birmingham
OL,7,Fhave voted to strike after alleging
OL,8,Fbullying, harassment and threats of
OL,9,Fblacklisting.
OL,11,FThe workers are employed through Job &
OL,12,FTalent, a private recruitment firm
OL,13,Fthat supplies temporary staff to
OL,14,Fcompanies and public services.
OL,16,FWhile these agency workers carry out
OL,17,Fcouncil bin rounds, they are legally
OL,18,Femployed by Job & Talent, which
OL,19,Fmanages their contracts, pay, HR, and
OL,20,Ftraining.
