OL,3,CFresh bin strike as agency workers say
OL,4,Cthey're being bullied and threatened
OL,6,FJust 22 agency workers were eligible
OL,7,Fto vote in the ballot by Unite the
OL,8,FUnion, with 18 taking part and all 18
OL,9,Fvoting in favour of industrial action.
OL,11,FUnite said the result is likely to
OL,12,Fencourage more agency staff to come
OL,13,Fforward, claiming that fear and
OL,14,Fintimidation previously prevented some
OL,15,Ffrom participating.
OL,17,FThe strike could add further pressure
OL,18,Fto Birmingham's refuse service, which
OL,19,Fhas already been disrupted by a long-
OL,20,Frunning dispute involving directly
OL,21,Femployed bin workers.
