OL,3,CFresh bin strike as agency workers say
OL,4,Cthey're being bullied and threatened
OL,6,FThe ballot followed growing tensions
OL,7,Fwithin the council's waste service.
OL,9,FUnite said concerns escalated after
OL,10,Fvideo footage appeared to show a
OL,11,Fmanager telling agency staff they
OL,12,Fcould be barred from permanent council
OL,13,Fjobs if they refused to cross picket
OL,14,Flines.
OL,16,FThe union accused the council of
OL,17,Ffailing to properly act on warnings
OL,18,Fraised by workers.
