OL,6,FJob & Talent strongly rejects the
OL,7,Fallegation. The company said:
OL,8,F"Following an immediate investigation
OL,9,Fby Birmingham City Council, it has
OL,10,Fbeen confirmed that no blacklisting
OL,11,Ftook place."
OL,13,FResponding to news of the latest
OL,14,Findustrial action, a spokesperson
OL,15,Fadded: "We acknowledge the ballot
OL,16,Foutcome and will continue to engage
OL,17,Fwith staff to address any issues
OL,18,Fraised.
