OL,3,CFresh bin strike as agency workers say
OL,4,Cthey're being bullied and threatened
OL,6,FOne worker told Unite: "Management try
OL,7,Fand give you extra work every day,
OL,8,Feven if you genuinely don't have the
OL,9,Ftime to do it they will force you to
OL,10,Fdo it.
OL,12,F"If you speak up for yourself and your
OL,13,Fcolleagues and if they don't like what
OL,14,Fthey hear it's one phone call to the
OL,15,Fagency and you're gone.
OL,17,F"It's a really toxic environment. The
OL,18,Fway the managers speak to you is rude,
OL,19,Fthere is no respect. You're not talked
OL,20,Fto like a person and there's constant
OL,21,Fpressure."
