OL,3,CFresh bin strike as agency workers say
OL,4,Cthey're being bullied and threatened
OL,6,FUnite general secretary Sharon Graham
OL,7,Fsaid: "This is a real escalation in
OL,8,Fthe dispute, with agency workers now
OL,9,Fjoining picket lines due to the
OL,10,Fterrible way they have been treated by
OL,11,FJob & Talent and Birmingham council.
OL,13,F"Birmingham Council is spending money
OL,14,Fit doesn't have on a dispute that
OL,15,Fcould be resolved by agreeing a fair
OL,16,Fdeal for workers.
